title: Fan, 1876
creditline: Gift of Mrs. John Innes Kane
description: Leaf of white silk with the obverse decorated with a spray of orange blossoms and a monogram: "SS April 26, 1876" painted in gouache. Reverse is blank. Sticks are plain white celluloid.
